@mheon playing around in 1.2.0, while a container is running I see no matching file in `/var/run/libpod/exits/$CID`.  After the container exits, but before I remove it, I see:
``/var/run/libpod/exits/ad53df0c...f64b3-old``.

So in the case of this test, after the normal test code runs, I should NOT find a ``--tmpdir`` file called ``${CID}.old`` (presumably, because the container has not stopped)?
